  sugar: 3 g
  protein: 5 g
  fiber: 2 g
  sodium: 180 mg
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/caramelized-shallot-risotto-59d68d5330a03b46f524d622
time required: 50 minutes
cuisine: North America
